        <p><span class="strong"><strong>Skills:</strong></span> <a href="ch74s10.html#MonstersVermin29">Monstrous spiders</a> have a +4 racial bonus on <a href="ch16s03.html#CombinedSkills179">Hide</a> and <a href="ch16s03.html#CombinedSkills294">Spot</a> checks and a +8 racial bonus on <a href="ch16s03.html#CombinedSkills71">Climb</a> checks. A <a href="ch74s10.html#MonstersVermin29">monstrous spider</a> can always choose to take 10 on <a href="ch16s03.html#CombinedSkills71">Climb</a> checks, even if rushed or threatened. <a href="ch74s10.html#MonstersVermin29">Monstrous spiders</a> use either their Strength or Dexterity modifier for <a href="ch16s03.html#CombinedSkills71">Climb</a> checks, whichever is higher. *Hunting spiders have a +10 racial bonus on <a href="ch16s03.html#CombinedSkills192">Jump</a> checks and a +8 racial bonus on <a href="ch16s03.html#CombinedSkills294">Spot</a> checks. Web-spinning spiders have a +8 racial bonus on <a href="ch16s03.html#CombinedSkills179">Hide</a> and <a href="ch16s03.html#CombinedSkills211">Move Silently</a> checks when using their webs.</p>
